47 AM / in 15 minutes BRIEF-Evolus Announces Pricing Of Initial Public Offering Of Common Stock Reuters Staff 
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Evolus Inc: 
* EVOLUS, INC. ANNOUNCES PRICING OF INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING OF COMMON STOCK 
* SAYS INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING OF 5.00 MILLION COMMON SHARES PRICED AT $12.00PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
